t=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613608\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hwj1665703064363.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hwj1665703064363.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hwj1665703064363.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hwj1665703064363\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n FRM Widget Type (Entity) \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Widget used to represent the entity occurrences in the component. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">OCCLIST</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">Grid</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hwj1665703064363__section_w6ab1b5b1_w7ab1b5_w8ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hwj1665703064363__table_d11933e1_d11934e1_d11935e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hwj1665703064363__table_d11933e1_d11934e1_d11935e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hwj1665703064363__table_d11933e1_d11934e1_d11935e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwj1665703064363__table_d11933e1_d11934e1_d11935e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">OCCLIST</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwj1665703064363__table_d11933e1_d11934e1_d11935e1__entry__2\">\n Display the entity as a list of occurrences.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwj1665703064363__table_d11933e1_d11934e1_d11935e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Grid</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwj1665703064363__table_d11933e1_d11934e1_d11935e1__entry__2\">\n Use the Grid widget. Each field represents a column in the grid and occurrences are represented as rows. The grid widget provides extended triggers that enable you to sort columns and resize the grid.\n <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"hwj1665703064363__note_w9ab1b5b1b3b3b7b3b3b1_w10ab1b5b1b3b3b7b3b3_w11ab1b5b1b3b3b7b3_w12ab1b5b1b3b3b7_w13ab1b5b1b3b3_w14ab1b5b1b3_w15ab1b5b1_w16ab1b5_w17ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The grid widget is not suitable for extremely large numbers of rows or columns, for example more than 60,000-120,000 cells.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hwj1665703064363__section_hsk_wwp_5wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d640007e131\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hwj1665703064363__ul_xk2_xwp_5wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hwj1665703064363__li_d39704e1_d39705e1_d39706e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uqv1665702561461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uqv1665702561461.html\" title=\"An Entity is an abstract data type that defines a logical data aggregation and its associated default characteristics and behavior. It may be mapped to a table in a DBMS, and is most frequently used to represent the application data, but it can also represent transient data, a collection of controls, or constant data.\">Entity</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/clg1695282025414.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>egrid (Grid)</a><p>The egrid widget displays data in a tabular format, in which the rows are occurrences of an entity and the columns are fields. It is an entity-level widget that is only applicable to form components.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613608\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613608\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "FRM Widget Type (Entity) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 FRM Widget Type (Entity) Widget used to represent the entity occurrences in the component. Valid values are OCCLIST and Grid . Value Description OCCLIST Display the entity as a list of occurrences. Grid Use the Grid widget. Each field represents a column in the grid and occurrences are represented as rows. The grid widget provides extended triggers that enable you to sort columns and resize the grid. Note: The grid widget is not suitable for extremely large numbers of rows or columns, for example more than 60,000-120,000 cells. Applies To Entity Related Links egrid (Grid) The egrid widget displays data in a tabular format, in which the rows are occurrences of an entity and the columns are fields. It is an entity-level widget that is only applicable to form components. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}